'''陸希未'''是一位[[小說家|小說家]]，代表作是《傳奇系列》（Legend）。[[CBS電影|CBS電影]]將《傳奇系列》改編成[[電影|電影]]<ref name="publishersweekly1">{{cite web|last=De Groot|first=Kate|url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/authors/profiles/article/49909-fall-2011-flying-starts-marie-lu.html |title=Fall 2011 Flying Starts: Marie Lu|publisher=[[Publishers_Weekly|Publishers Weekly]]|date=December 19, 2011|accessdate=February 19, 2014}}</ref>由[[喬納森·萊文|喬納森·萊文]]執導<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jonathan-levine-tapped-direct-cbs-188041 |title=Jonathan Levine Tapped to Direct CBS Films' 'Legend'|publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=May 12, 2011|accessdate=February 19, 2014}}</ref>。

==生涯==
1984年，陸希未出生在[[中國|中國]][[無錫|無錫]]，後來搬到[[北京|北京]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Lu |first=Marie |url=https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4342215.Marie_Lu |title=Marie Lu (Author of Legend) |work=[[Goodreads|Goodreads]] |publisher=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] |date= |accessdate=December 12, 2014 |archive-date=2019-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410222420/https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4342215.Marie_Lu |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theaudiobookstore.com/marie-lu/prodigy-legend-novel-book_b00attaj26.aspx|title=Prodigy: A Legend Novel Audiobook|publisher=The Audiobook Store|accessdate=December 12, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213013811/http://www.theaudiobookstore.com/marie-lu/prodigy-legend-novel-book_b00attaj26.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1989年，陸希未舉家搬到美國[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://marielu.org/marie.html|title=Marie Lu - About|accessdate=February 19, 2014|archive-date=2010-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101230203100/http://marielu.org/marie.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當時中國爆發[[六四天安門事件|六四天安門事件]]<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.pbs.org/wnet/tavissmiley/interviews/novelist-marie-lu/| title = Novelist Marie Lu| website = [[PBS.org|PBS.org]]| language = en-US| accessdate = 2016-02-29}}</ref>。陸希未之後就讀[[南加州大學|南加州大學]]，也在[[迪斯尼互動工作室|迪斯尼互動工作室]]實習<ref name="publishersweekly1"/>。


